msgctxt "sn35.154:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 35 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 35 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.154:0.2"
msgid "15. Navapurāṇavagga "
msgstr "15. The Old and the New "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 154. Indriyasampannasutta → indriya (pts1)
msgctxt "sn35.154:0.3"
msgid "154. Indriyasampannasutta "
msgstr "154. Endowed With Faculties "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn35.154:1.1"
msgid "Atha kho aññataro bhikkhu yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami … pe … ekamantaṃ nisinno kho so bhikkhu bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then a mendicant went up to the Buddha … and asked him, "

msgctxt "sn35.154:1.2"
msgid "“‘indriyasampanno, indriyasampanno’ti, bhante, vuccati. "
msgstr "“Sir, they speak of someone who is ‘accomplished regarding the faculties’. "

msgctxt "sn35.154:1.3"
msgid "Kittāvatā nu kho, bhante, indriyasampanno hotī”ti? "
msgstr "How is someone accomplished regarding the faculties defined?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn35.154:2.1"
msgid "“Cakkhundriye ce, bhikkhu, udayabbayānupassī viharanto cakkhundriye nibbindati … pe … "
msgstr "“Mendicant, if someone meditates observing rise and fall in the eye faculty, they grow disillusioned with the eye faculty. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.154:2.2"
msgid "jivhindriye ce, bhikkhu, udayabbayānupassī viharanto jivhindriye nibbindati … pe … "
msgstr "If they meditate observing rise and fall in the ear faculty … nose faculty … tongue faculty … body faculty … "

msgctxt "sn35.154:2.3"
msgid "manindriye ce, bhikkhu, udayabbayānupassī viharanto manindriye nibbindati. "
msgstr "mind faculty, they grow disillusioned with the mind faculty. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.154:2.4"
msgid "Nibbindaṃ virajjati … pe … vimuttasmiṃ vimuttamiti ñāṇaṃ hoti. "
msgstr "Being disillusioned, desire fades away. … When they’re freed, they know they’re freed. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.154:2.5"
msgid "‘Khīṇā jāti, vusitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ, kataṃ karaṇīyaṃ, nāparaṃ itthattāyā’ti pajānāti. "
msgstr "They understand: ‘Rebirth is ended, the spiritual journey has been completed, what had to be done has been done, there is no return to any state of existence.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.154:2.6"
msgid "Ettāvatā kho, bhikkhu, indriyasampanno hotī”ti. "
msgstr "This is how someone who is accomplished regarding the faculties is defined.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn35.154:2.7"
msgid "Navamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

